<h2>Google Business Profile for Tattoo Shops</h2>
<p>Your <a href="/blog/optimize-google-business-profile/">Google Business Profile</a> determines whether you appear in the map pack when someone searches "tattoo shop near me." <a href="https://www.brightlocal.com/resources/local-seo-statistics/">42% of local searchers click on map pack results</a>. Businesses with complete profiles are <a href="https://support.google.com/business">70% more likely to attract in-person visits</a>.</p>
<h3>Set Up Your GBP Right</h3>
<ul>
<li>[ ] <strong>Primary category:</strong> "Tattoo Shop" (most specific available)</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Secondary categories:</strong> "Body Piercing Shop" (if you offer piercings), "Art Studio"</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Business description:</strong> 750 characters. Lead with your styles, location, and what makes your shop different</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Services:</strong> List every service (custom tattoos, flash, cover-ups, piercings, tattoo removal consultations)</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Business hours:</strong> Include walk-in hours if different from appointment hours</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Phone number:</strong> Local number, not toll-free</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Website:</strong> Link to your homepage or booking page</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Booking link:</strong> Add a direct link to your online booking system</li>
<li>[ ] <strong>Attributes:</strong> Wheelchair accessible, appointment required, walk-ins welcome, LGBTQ+ friendly</li>
</ul>
<p>For more on choosing the right <a href="/blog/gbp-categories-guide/">GBP categories</a>, see our detailed guide.</p>
